               <scopecontent id="aspace_e80bdd77946b785a356ce5a011a919ca">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Contains 17 autograph manuscript poems, unsigned, by Guy Debord sent over several weeks to Michèle Bernstein following a breakup in 1964 under the title <title>
                        <part>Épopée Léwinienne</part>
                     </title>. Also contains 5 additional poems by Debord created around the same time but that are not part of the <title>
                        <part>Épopée Léwinienne</part>
                     </title>. Accompanied by a manuscript notebook written by Bernstein providing explanations of the poems.</p>
               </scopecontent>
